data.name: textBox1.Text
data.value: Welcome to Pahuway! Please take a moment to review our simple rules. Pay when you order, our prices include taxes. Check our hours online or call. We don't take regular reservations, but special events may have them. Seating is first come, first served, so be considerate during busy times. We offer free Wi-Fi, but please use it responsibly. Respect others, and no harassment is allowed. Only our food and drinks are permitted; outside items are not. Follow any health and safety rules in place. We're not responsible for lost items. Well-behaved pets are welcome outside, if allowed by local rules. Families are welcome, but please supervise your kids. Special events may have their own rules. Share your thoughts with us. These rules can change, so check our website for updates.
